profile: Beach One Flooring gives the customer a personalized shop at home service. Daryl & Steve come to you with a wide selection of products they themselves can install for you or they can provide you with tips and tricks for the do it your self homeowner. With Beach One Flooring you deal directly with a father and son team with over 38 years of combined experience. Both are union certified installers and WSIB compliant. With their extensive experience and no middle man, Steve and Daryl can work to your budget. Give them a call today for a free inspection and quote.
